  "YangsThoughts": "Riley Centrella sent a team to Solaris VII in 3062 to set up Firefly Stables. This was the first thing Firefly Foundry built specifically for them, eleven years later. A 200 XXL engine in a 25-ton frame costs more than some assault mechs to maintain and the armor is basically paint. The PPC Capacitor on a Light PPC is experimental and the Rocket Launcher is single-use. It was built for the arena and nowhere else.",
